cs.LO, cs.PL, cs.AI, cs.SE, cs.DS

The paper discusses a bounded model checker that supports different logic languages, which is a topic related to logic and programming languages (cs.LO). The tool also uses PLTL and TRIO, which are logic languages (cs.PL). The paper mentions the tool's ability to support different encodings of temporal logic, which is a topic related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the tool's extendibility and modifiability, which are topics related to software engineering (cs.SE) and data structures (cs.DS).
